      "instruction": "<p>Once the pork is ready, transfer it to a clean chopping board and slice into 2 slices per person</p><p>Serve the <strong>Filipino-style pork belly slices</strong> topped with the <strong>cooked onion</strong> and <strong>stock</strong> from the foil parcel</p><p>Serve the <strong>garlic rice</strong> and <strong>pineapple salsa</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
